Text.string: You're about to have a bad day, mate!
You're a big one, ain't ya?
Can't say I didn't warn ya!
And that's the [deeper masculine shout] T!
Score one for the good guys!
I'm a right asshole when I haven't had my coffee.
For the king! I'm the king, in case you were wondering.
You'll have to do better than that!
I love it when they pop like that!
You're a right shambles now, eh?
A little help from my friends...
Hey, I nicked some meds, have one.
Not the best time for a kip, mate!
Come on, get back to it!
And leave me holdin' the bag? Not bloody likely!
Be with you in a tick!
Let's give you a proper send-off!
Never mess with a bloke who worked retail!
Come on, let's have a go!
Oi! Here when you need me!
Could really use an espresso or three...
Don't pop your clogs just yet.
Keep calm and kill something, eh?
Let's try turning you off and on again.
Lucky for you I dated a bloke in I-T.
What? You need a spoonful of sugar or summat?
Knew you had it in you!
Faff about on your own time.
Let's just say you owe me one.
